@NODE 5. "Requirements"

        Besides what comes with this archive, the AlphaSpell GUI requires
AlphaSpell, reqtools.library, rexxreqtools.library, and Varexx v1.6. All of
these are available on the Aminet:

    AlphaSpell - /text/edit/ASpell.lha
    Varexx - /util/rexx/varexx.lha

        AlphaSpell is also available from the official AlphaSpell
@{"support" LINK 8.} site on BitNova.

@ENDNODE

